---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Le Studio — Collectif Cobalt"
  description="Studio de design d'espace et d'architecture d'intérieur en Nouvelle-Aquitaine. Angoulême · Bordeaux · Bayonne."
  current="studio"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-num" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
    <div class="hero-label sr">Le Studio</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title sr">
      COBALT<span class="serif-it">+</span><br />
      STUDIO.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-desc sr sr-d2">
      Studio de design d'espace et d'architecture d'intérieur basé en Nouvelle-Aquitaine. Trois designers diplômés —
      des intérieurs justes, des matières honnêtes, des espaces qui durent.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions sr sr-d3">
      <a href="/projets" class="btn btn-cream"><span>Voir les projets →</span></a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:var(--cream); border-color:rgba(240,235,216,.4)">
        <span>Nous contacter</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARQUEE -->
  <div class="marquee-wrap">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span class="marquee-item">
        <span class="hi">cobalt.</span><span class="marquee-sep"></span>Design d'espace<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Architecture d'intérieur<span class="marquee-sep"></span><span class="hi">Nouvelle-Aquitaine</span><span class="marquee-sep"></span>Réhabilitation<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Mobilier sur mesure<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Matières locales<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Angoulême · Bordeaux · Bayonne<span class="marquee-sep"></span>
      </span>
      <span class="marquee-item">
        <span class="hi">cobalt.</span><span class="marquee-sep"></span>Design d'espace<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Architecture d'intérieur<span class="marquee-sep"></span><span class="hi">Nouvelle-Aquitaine</span><span class="marquee-sep"></span>Réhabilitation<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Mobilier sur mesure<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Matières locales<span class="marquee-sep"></span>Angoulême · Bordeaux · Bayonne<span class="marquee-sep"></span>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats-wrap">
    <div class="stat-cell sr">
      <div class="stat-num" data-target="3">3</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">Designers diplômés</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell sr sr-d1">
      <div class="stat-num" data-target="6">6</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">Projets livrés</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell sr sr-d2">
      <div class="stat-num" data-target="5">5</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">Départements couverts</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell sr sr-d3">
      <div class="stat-num">100<span style="font-size:.5em">%</span></div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">Nouvelle-Aquitaine</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FEATURED PROJECTS -->
  <section class="featured">
    <div class="feat-header sr">
      <div>
        <div class="s-label">Réalisations sélectionnées</div>
        <h2 class="feat-title">PROJETS<br />RÉCENTS.</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/projets" class="feat-link">Tous les projets →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-grid sr sr-d1">
      <a href="/projets/angouleme" class="feat-card feat-main">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618221195710-dd6b41faaea6?w=1200&q=85&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Appartement Angoulême" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="feat-overlay"></div>
        <div class="feat-meta">
          <h3 class="feat-card-title">Appartement Angoulême.</h3>
          <div class="feat-info">
            <span>Angoulême</span><span>95 m²</span><span>2024</span>
            <span class="badge badge-livré">Livré</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/projets/bordeaux" class="feat-card feat-side">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565182999561-18d7dc61c393?w=900&q=85&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Atelier Bordeaux" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="feat-overlay"></div>
        <div class="feat-meta">
          <h3 class="feat-card-title">Atelier Bordeaux.</h3>
          <div class="feat-info">
            <span>Bordeaux</span><span>210 m²</span><span>2024</span>
            <span class="badge badge-livré">Livré</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/projets/bayonne" class="feat-card feat-side">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?w=900&q=85&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Boutique Bayonne" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="feat-overlay"></div>
        <div class="feat-meta">
          <h3 class="feat-card-title">Boutique Bayonne.</h3>
          <div class="feat-info">
            <span>Bayonne</span><span>85 m²</span><span>2023</span>
            <span class="badge badge-livré">Livré</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MANIFESTE STRIP -->
  <div class="manifeste-strip">
    <div class="ms-left sr">
      <div>
        <div class="s-label on-dark">Notre positionnement</div>
        <h2 class="ms-title">PENSER.<br />FAIRE.<br />TRANSMETTRE.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="ms-year">2026</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ms-right sr sr-d2">
      <div class="ms-body">
        <p>Nous sommes designers d'espace et d'architecture d'intérieur — pas architectes. C'est un choix autant qu'un cadre légal. Notre terrain, c'est l'intérieur : la façon dont un espace est vécu, traversé, habité.</p>
        <p>Nous croyons que le design d'espace bien fait change la qualité de vie. Un appartement redistribué, un restaurant dont le mobilier transforme une soirée, un atelier converti en espace de création — ces projets ont un impact réel, immédiat, quotidien.</p>
        <p>Notre territoire, c'est la Nouvelle-Aquitaine. Ses matériaux, ses artisans, ses paysages.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-cream" style="margin-top:40px"><span>Démarrer un projet →</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style is:global>
  /* Styles spécifiques à la page Studio (extraits de studio.html) */
  .stripe { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bleu) 25%, var(--noir) 25% 50%, var(--bleu) 50% 75%, var(--noir) 75%); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh; background: var(--noir);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 140px 44px 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(240,235,216,.1);
  }
  .hero-bg-num {
    position: absolute; right: -60px; bottom: -80px;
    font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(300px,40vw,500px);
    color: rgba(74,130,220,.07); line-height: 1; pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
  }
  .hero-label {
    font-size: .62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bleu); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-label::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--bleu); }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: clamp(72px, 12vw, 160px);
    line-height: .84; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .hero-title .serif-it {
    font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic;
    color: var(--bleu); font-weight: 400;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    max-width: 560px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(240,235,216,.5); margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* STATS */
  .stats-wrap {
    background: var(--noir);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr);
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(240,235,216,.06);
  }
  .stat-cell {
    padding: 52px 44px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(240,235,216,.06);
  }
  .stat-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: clamp(52px,6vw,80px);
    line-height: 1; color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .stat-lbl { font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(240,235,216,.3); }

  /* FEATURED PROJECTS */
  .featured { padding: 100px 44px; }
  .feat-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .feat-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(40px,5vw,64px); line-height: .9; }
  .feat-link { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bleu); transition: color .15s; }
  .feat-link:hover { color: var(--noir); }
  .feat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .feat-main { grid-row: span 2; }
  .feat-card {
    position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--r-md);
    background: var(--noir); display: block;
  }
  .feat-card img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform .6s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94);
  }
  .feat-main { height: 580px; }
  .feat-side { height: 280px; }
  .feat-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .feat-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26,26,26,.9) 0%, transparent 55%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .feat-meta { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; padding: 28px 32px; }
  .feat-card-title {
    font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem,2.5vw,2rem); color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px);
    transition: opacity .35s, transform .35s;
  }
  .feat-card:hover .feat-card-title { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .feat-info {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: .6rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(240,235,216,.5);
  }
  .badge { padding: 3px 10px; font-size: .56rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; border-radius: 4px; }
  .badge-livré { background: var(--vert); color: var(--cream); }
  .badge-cours { background: var(--jaune); color: var(--noir); }

  /* MANIFESTE STRIP */
  .manifeste-strip {
    background: var(--noir); padding: 100px 44px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px;
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(240,235,216,.06);
  }
  .ms-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
  .ms-year { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(80px,10vw,140px); line-height: 1; color: rgba(240,235,216,.06); }
  .ms-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(36px,4vw,56px); line-height: .9; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .ms-body p { font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(240,235,216,.5); margin-bottom: 20px; }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .hero { padding: 110px 20px 56px; min-height: 0; }
    .hero-title { font-size: clamp(56px, 12vw, 110px); margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: .92rem; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero-actions { gap: 12px; }
    .stats-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .stat-cell { padding: 40px 28px; }
    .stat-cell:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
    .stat-cell:nth-child(1), .stat-cell:nth-child(2) { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,235,216,.06); }
    .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .feat-main { height: 400px; }
    .feat-side { height: 240px; }
    .feat-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .featured { padding: 64px 20px; }
    .feat-meta { padding: 22px 24px; }
    .manifeste-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; padding: 64px 20px; }
    .ms-year { font-size: clamp(64px, 18vw, 100px); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .hero { padding: 96px 18px 48px; }
    .hero-title { font-size: clamp(52px, 14vw, 84px); }
    .hero-desc { font-size: .85rem; line-height: 1.75; }
    .hero-actions { gap: 10px; }
    .stat-cell { padding: 32px 20px; }
    .stat-num { font-size: clamp(40px, 12vw, 56px); }
    .stat-lbl { font-size: .6rem; }
    .featured { padding: 52px 16px; }
    .feat-main { height: 320px; }
    .feat-side { height: 200px; }
    .feat-meta { padding: 18px 20px; }
    .feat-card-title { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .manifeste-strip { padding: 52px 18px; gap: 28px; }
    .ms-title { font-size: clamp(32px, 9vw, 44px); margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .ms-body p { font-size: .85rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  }
</style>
